latestPosts.caption:
My SKIN is the only thing that got better this year 🫶
.
The journey of my skin this entire year. And if you do things right it will get better. Couldn’t have done it without the right product, knowledge I got from watching lots of YT videos and doing research and key skincare advice from my friend @andre.jagtap 

I dint go to any doctor, did not do any fancy treatment’s and I was very sure I did not want to take pills. I wanted to clear it myself with the right skincare routine and lifestyle changes that’s the most sustainable. It definitely took time and I was ready for it. 
.
The product that I got the most impactful result from is the @paulaschoicein 2% Salicylic acid liquid exfoliant. But my whole skincare routine has been a game changer, which I’m very happy about. I realized my acne was because of clogged pores and build up of dead skin cells which I wasn’t getting rid of. And that’s where the BHA really helped. Salicylic acid is a must in your skincare routine if you have combination to oily acne prone skin.
